# Feature-Sliced Design (FSD) Architecture Rules

This project follows **Feature-Sliced Design (FSD)** architecture pattern. Follow these rules strictly:

## Layer Hierarchy & Dependencies

**CRITICAL**: Dependencies flow ONLY upward (unidirectional):

```
app в†‘ pages в†‘ widgets в†‘ features в†‘ entities в†‘ shared
```

### Layer Rules:

- **`app`**: Application initialization (providers, global styles, router)
- **`pages`**: Page components mapping to application routes
- **`widgets`**: Large UI blocks combining features. Can import from `features`, `entities`, `shared`
- **`features`**: User interactions (verbs). Can import from `entities`, `shared` ONLY
- **`entities`**: Business objects (nouns). Can import from `shared` ONLY
- **`shared`**: Reusable utilities, UI kit, API clients. Cannot import from any other layer

### Slice Rules:

- Slices on the same layer **CANNOT** import from each other
- Each slice must have an `index.ts` file as its public API
- Always import from barrel files: `import { Component } from '@/features/authenticate-user'`
- Never deep import: `import { Component } from '@/features/authenticate-user/ui/Component'`

## File Structure Patterns

### Required Segments in Each Slice:

- `ui/`: React components and presentation logic
- `model/`: Business logic, state management, hooks
- `api/`: External API interactions (GraphQL, REST)
- `lib/`: Slice-specific utilities
- `config/`: Constants and configuration

## File Naming Conventions

**CRITICAL**: Follow consistent naming for code clarity.

- **Folders (Slices)**: `kebab-case` в†’ `assign-script`, `talent-profile`
- **React Components**: `PascalCase.tsx` в†’ `TalentAvatar.tsx`, `ScriptDashboard.tsx`
- **Custom Hooks**: `useCamelCase.ts` в†’ `useTalent.ts`, `useAssignScript.ts`
- **Utilities/Logic**: `kebab-case.ts` в†’ `format-date.ts`, `parse-jwt.ts`
- **API Files**: `kebab-case.query.ts`, `kebab-case.mutation.ts` в†’ `get-talent.query.ts`, `assign-script.mutation.ts`
- **Public API**: Always `index.ts` as barrel file

вњ… **Correct:**

```typescript
features/assign-script/
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ui/AssignScriptButton.tsx
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ model/useAssignScript.ts
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ api/assign-script.mutation.ts
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ index.ts
```

вќЊ **Incorrect:**

```typescript
features/AssignScript/          // вќЊ Wrong: camelCase folder
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ui/AssignScriptButton.tsx // вќЊ Wrong: camelCase file
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ model/UseAssignScript.ts  // вќЊ Wrong: PascalCase hook
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ api/assign_script.mutation.ts // вќЊ Wrong: snake_case
```

See [naming-conventions.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/naming-conventions.mdc) for full details.

