## Import Patterns

### Correct Imports:

```typescript
// вњ… Import from barrel files
import { Button } from "@/shared/ui";
import { useUserProfile } from "@/entities/user";
import { Login } from "@/features/auth";

// вњ… Layer-appropriate imports
// In features/auth/ui/Login.tsx:
import { Button } from "@/shared/ui"; // вњ… shared
import { useUserProfile } from "@/entities/user"; // вњ… entities
```

### Forbidden Imports:

```typescript
// вќЊ Deep imports
import { Button } from "@/shared/ui/button/button";

// вќЊ Cross-layer violations
// In shared/lib/utils.ts:
import { Login } from "@/features/auth"; // вќЊ shared cannot import features

// вќЊ Same-layer imports
// In features/authenticate-user/ui/Login.tsx:
import { ApproveButton } from "@/features/approve"; // вќЊ features cannot import features
```

## Component Organization

- **Entities**: Pure data models and API hooks (nouns)
- **Features**: User interactions and business actions (verbs)
- **Widgets**: Composition of multiple features and entities
- **Shared**: Generic, reusable components and utilities

## Public API Requirements

Every slice MUST export through `index.ts`:

```typescript
// features/authenticate-user/index.ts
export { Login } from "./ui/Login";
export { useMsalEvent } from "./lib/useMsalEvent";
export { msalConfig } from "./lib/msalConfig";
```

